snippet.title: Misericorde: Volume One Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
As an Anchoress, Sister Hedwig took an oath to never leave her cell; to devote herself entirely to God and provide spiritual support to all who came to her door. But as the only Sister who couldn't possibly have committed the crime, she have a new mission: solve the case, before the bishop shutters the convent and the real killer goes unpunished.

Misericorde: Volume One is the first entry in a multi-part VN series and releases March 24, 2023!
